1
00:01:14,249 --> 00:01:17,252
Demam awak dah kebah?

2
00:01:21,214 --> 00:01:22,215
Terima kasih.

3
00:01:26,177 --> 00:01:27,553
Kita akan lewat nanti.

4
00:01:27,637 --> 00:01:28,554
Apa?

5
00:01:38,690 --> 00:01:40,358
- Jom.
- Apa?

6
00:01:41,776 --> 00:01:43,069
Okey.

7
00:01:45,863 --> 00:01:47,240
Nak saya pegangkan?

8
00:01:48,783 --> 00:01:50,034
- Boleh.
- Okey.

9
00:02:04,132 --> 00:02:05,341
Bagus.

10
00:02:06,009 --> 00:02:08,052
Sol-i, awak nak jadi ketua kelas?

11
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:11,681
Awak selalu tiru kerja sekolah,
tidur dalam kelas

12
00:02:11,764 --> 00:02:13,391
dan tak pernah beri perhatian…

13
00:02:13,474 --> 00:02:15,101
- Tangkap!
- Tapi

14
00:02:15,184 --> 00:02:17,979
bukan awak seorang saja yang teruk.

15
00:02:18,062 --> 00:02:20,440
Tiada siapa yang layak pegang jawatan itu.

16
00:02:20,523 --> 00:02:22,483
Woo Dae-sung jarang hadir.

17
00:02:22,567 --> 00:02:25,236
Cha Heon pula tentu tak kenal
rakan kelasnya sendiri.

18
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:27,488
Ha-young pula…

19
00:02:30,867 --> 00:02:32,744
Heon, awak sibuk tak?

20
00:02:33,619 --> 00:02:35,747
Saya dah tulis ucapan ketua kelas.

21
00:02:36,331 --> 00:02:37,498
Boleh tolong baca?

22
00:02:37,582 --> 00:02:39,751
Okey. Saya baca kemudian.

23
00:02:39,834 --> 00:02:41,085
Okey.

24
00:02:41,169 --> 00:02:43,171
Takkan awak nak putus asa?

25
00:02:43,254 --> 00:02:46,799
Buah hati awak, Cha Heon, akan jadi
wakil pelajar dengan si Hui-ji itu.

26
00:02:46,883 --> 00:02:48,509
Awak nak biarkan saja?

27
00:02:49,886 --> 00:02:51,137
Tak, bukan?

28
00:02:51,220 --> 00:02:54,098
"Helo, saya Shin Sol-i!"

29
00:02:54,932 --> 00:02:58,144
"Helo, saya Shin Sol-i."

30
00:02:58,227 --> 00:03:01,481
"Helo, saya Shin Sol-i."

31
00:03:02,982 --> 00:03:05,943
Betul. Tentulah mereka kenal saya.

32
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:09,864
Oh, Tuhan!

33
00:03:09,947 --> 00:03:11,699
Kenapa awak nampak lesu hari ini?

34
00:03:11,783 --> 00:03:13,534
Biasanya awak ceria saja.

35
00:03:13,618 --> 00:03:15,870
Kenapa awak tak bersemangat?

36
00:03:15,953 --> 00:03:17,246
Biar saya baca.

37
00:03:18,831 --> 00:03:21,334
"Saya, Shin Sol-i, akan curahkan

38
00:03:21,417 --> 00:03:24,337
seluruh jiwa raga dan kesetiaan saya
kepada Kelas 1-7."

39
00:03:26,297 --> 00:03:27,507
"Saya, Wang Se-hyeong,

40
00:03:28,299 --> 00:03:31,010
akan curahkan seluruh jiwa raga

41
00:03:31,511 --> 00:03:34,931
dan kesetiaan saya kepada Kelas 1-7."

42
00:03:35,014 --> 00:03:39,644
- Wang Se-hyeong!
- Wang Se-hyeong!

43
00:03:39,727 --> 00:03:42,814
- Undilah Wang Se-hyeong!
- Undilah Wang Se-hyeong!

44
00:03:43,648 --> 00:03:46,275
Se-hyeong, boleh belikan roti lagi?

45
00:03:47,443 --> 00:03:49,904
Awak tak tiru ucapan Se-hyeong, bukan?

46
00:03:50,738 --> 00:03:52,407
Awak sertai kelas tuisyen yang sama?

47
00:03:53,991 --> 00:03:56,494
Habislah. Tak ada harapan.

48
00:04:05,211 --> 00:04:07,213
Jangan ikut ucapan yang terlalu biasa.

49
00:04:07,839 --> 00:04:09,674
Cuba fikir kelebihan awak.

50
00:04:11,467 --> 00:04:12,969
Mungkin saya patut tarik diri.

51
00:04:13,052 --> 00:04:14,178
Jangan risau.

52
00:04:14,762 --> 00:04:17,140
Saya yakin kawan saya ini ada kelebihan.

53
00:04:17,223 --> 00:04:18,349
Apa dia?

54
00:04:19,183 --> 00:04:20,226
Keikhlasan.

55
00:04:21,394 --> 00:04:23,312
Apa? Keikhlasan?

56
00:04:24,647 --> 00:04:27,191
Sekarang mungkin awak dipandang remeh,

57
00:04:27,275 --> 00:04:30,111
tapi awak akan buat
yang terbaik lepas ini, bukan?

58
00:04:30,194 --> 00:04:31,070
Betul.

59
00:04:31,154 --> 00:04:34,157
Itu dah memadai untuk jadi
ketua kelas yang hebat.

60
00:04:35,741 --> 00:04:37,452
Ini pujian atau kutukan?

61
00:04:42,415 --> 00:04:43,916
Kawan.

62
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,461
Pemahaman awak sangat menakjubkan.

63
00:04:49,005 --> 00:04:50,506
Hei, Woo Dae-sung!

64
00:05:01,184 --> 00:05:02,852
Apa itu?

65
00:05:02,935 --> 00:05:04,437
- Apa?
- Tengok!

66
00:05:09,233 --> 00:05:10,860
CALON KETUA KELAS
OH HUI-JI, SHIN SOL-I, WANG SE-HYEONG

67
00:05:15,031 --> 00:05:16,073
Heon!

68
00:05:16,824 --> 00:05:18,993
- Ada apa?
- Siapa yang awak akan undi?

69
00:05:21,787 --> 00:05:23,664
Jangan! Jangan jawab.

70
00:05:24,207 --> 00:05:25,833
Kita tak boleh dedahkan undi kita.

71
00:05:25,917 --> 00:05:27,084
Okey?

72
00:05:27,668 --> 00:05:30,922
Apa pun, saya akan bekerja keras.
Berilah sokongan awak.

73
00:05:32,548 --> 00:05:35,426
HARI UNDIAN KETUA KELAS

74
00:05:39,263 --> 00:05:42,099
Cikgu dan kawan sekalian, apa khabar?

75
00:05:42,892 --> 00:05:44,769
Saya Shin Sol-i.

76
00:05:44,852 --> 00:05:48,105
Saya percaya tentu kawan-kawan

77
00:05:48,773 --> 00:05:50,149
yang terkejut dan tak percaya

78
00:05:50,233 --> 00:05:53,819
dengan keputusan saya untuk bertanding.

79
00:05:54,403 --> 00:05:56,697
Prestasi saya lemah

80
00:05:56,781 --> 00:05:59,116
dan saya juga bukan pelajar cemerlang.

81
00:05:59,951 --> 00:06:03,037
Saya juga tiada sifat kepimpinan
dan tak menghiburkan.

82
00:06:05,706 --> 00:06:07,708
HELO, SAYA SHIN SOL-I…

83
00:06:09,085 --> 00:06:10,503
JANGAN PUTUS ASA!

84
00:06:12,213 --> 00:06:13,381
Bersemangatlah!

85
00:06:14,799 --> 00:06:15,925
Jangan putus asa!

86
00:06:23,516 --> 00:06:25,309
Saya banyak buat silap

87
00:06:25,393 --> 00:06:27,228
dan saya juga cemerkap.

88
00:06:27,812 --> 00:06:30,189
Tapi saya percaya ciri-ciri inilah

89
00:06:30,273 --> 00:06:34,318
yang membolehkan saya berubah
menjadi seorang yang lebih baik.

90
00:06:35,444 --> 00:06:40,157
Kita akan habiskan tempoh terpenting
dalam hidup kita bersama.

91
00:06:40,658 --> 00:06:45,037
Satu hari nanti, saya ingin dikenang
bukan sebagai Sol-i yang cemerkap,

92
00:06:45,121 --> 00:06:47,039
tapi ketua kelas kesayangan

93
00:06:47,123 --> 00:06:50,668
yang membantu semua orang
dan oleh itu saya berjanji,

94
00:06:51,711 --> 00:06:53,379
saya akan buat yang terbaik!

95
00:07:06,100 --> 00:07:07,143
Nah.

96
00:07:07,727 --> 00:07:10,021
Terima kasih kerana
tolong periksa ucapan saya.

97
00:07:10,104 --> 00:07:10,980
Tak perlulah.

98
00:07:11,063 --> 00:07:12,440
Terima sajalah.

99
00:07:12,523 --> 00:07:15,443
Hui-ji buat sendiri.
Tak manis kalau awak tolak.

100
00:07:18,404 --> 00:07:20,531
Dia terimalah!

101
00:07:20,615 --> 00:07:22,491
Tengok, penolong ketua kelas.

102
00:07:22,575 --> 00:07:24,035
Itu pun dah cukup bagus.

103
00:07:24,619 --> 00:07:26,203
Dia patut sedar diri.

104
00:07:26,287 --> 00:07:27,246
Janganlah macam ini.

105
00:07:27,330 --> 00:07:29,081
Apa salahnya?

106
00:07:32,168 --> 00:07:33,753
Macam mana dengan awak?

107
00:07:33,836 --> 00:07:35,463
Awak yang tak sedar diri.

108
00:07:36,631 --> 00:07:37,965
Sudahlah.

109
00:07:43,554 --> 00:07:45,931
Cakaplah. Kenapa awak tak undi Sol-i?

110
00:07:49,101 --> 00:07:50,519
Jawapannya dah jelas.

111
00:07:56,525 --> 00:07:59,028
2 JAM SEBELUM

112
00:07:59,111 --> 00:08:00,071
Okey.

113
00:08:00,571 --> 00:08:02,281
Hui-ji dan Sol-i seri.

114
00:08:04,241 --> 00:08:06,786
Cikgu, Cha Heon tak ada.

115
00:08:14,126 --> 00:08:15,127
Cha Heon.

116
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:18,714
Siapa yang awak akan undi?

117
00:08:19,465 --> 00:08:21,717
Hei, Cha Heon! Saya di sini.

118
00:08:21,801 --> 00:08:23,969
Jangan lupa kawan baik awak ini.

119
00:08:27,264 --> 00:08:28,307
Tolonglah…

120
00:08:29,517 --> 00:08:30,351
Oh Hui-ji.

121
00:08:53,666 --> 00:08:54,667
Heon!

122
00:08:55,626 --> 00:08:57,378
- Apa?
- Kenapa bukan saya?

123
00:08:57,461 --> 00:08:58,838
Awak tiada ciri-ciri ketua.

124
00:08:58,921 --> 00:09:00,256
Hui-ji pula ada?

125
00:09:01,590 --> 00:09:02,675
Berbanding awak, ya.

126
00:09:05,845 --> 00:09:06,846
Hei!

127
00:09:11,183 --> 00:09:13,519
Apa? Awak tendang Cha Heon?

128
00:09:13,602 --> 00:09:14,895
Kuat tak?

129
00:09:15,730 --> 00:09:17,314
Perlahanlah sikit.

130
00:09:17,398 --> 00:09:20,234
Saya langsung tak sangka
awak akan buat begitu.

131
00:09:20,317 --> 00:09:22,027
Dia dah terima pengajaran.

132
00:09:22,528 --> 00:09:24,989
Awak yang tendang dia,
tapi kenapa saya yang teruja?

133
00:09:26,198 --> 00:09:28,492
Fikiran saya bercelaru.

134
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,871
Adakah dia akan maafkan saya?

135
00:09:31,954 --> 00:09:33,622
Cha Heon, tunggu saya!

136
00:09:33,706 --> 00:09:35,916
Biar betul? Saya tak percaya.

137
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,334
Sol-i tendang awak?

138
00:09:37,418 --> 00:09:40,713
Sol-i! Shin Sol-i!

139
00:09:48,971 --> 00:09:51,515
Sol-i! Shin Sol-i!

140
00:09:51,599 --> 00:09:52,516
Ada apa?

141
00:09:53,058 --> 00:09:55,186
- Nah.
- Apa ini?

142
00:09:55,269 --> 00:09:57,688
Bayaran untuk baju sukan minggu depan.

143
00:09:57,772 --> 00:09:59,315
Hui-ji suruh beri kepada awak.

144
00:09:59,398 --> 00:10:00,649
- Saya?
- Entah.

145
00:10:02,485 --> 00:10:04,236
Dia serahkan tugas kepada awak.

146
00:10:05,196 --> 00:10:07,656
Ha-young, apa patut saya buat?

147
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:09,116
Apa maksud awak?

148
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,035
Awak penolong ketua kelas.

149
00:10:11,118 --> 00:10:13,287
Bukan. Maksud saya, Cha Heon.

150
00:10:13,370 --> 00:10:15,915
Macam mana saya nak
kutip bayaran daripada dia?

151
00:10:15,998 --> 00:10:17,917
Hei, minta saja.

152
00:10:18,751 --> 00:10:21,253
Letak sebelah tangan di bahu dan ugut dia.

153
00:10:21,337 --> 00:10:23,088
Begini. Suruh dia bayar.

154
00:10:25,299 --> 00:10:26,842
Saya rendah daripada dia.

155
00:10:28,761 --> 00:10:31,555
Buat ketika duduk.
Cha Heon sentiasa duduk.

156
00:10:34,350 --> 00:10:36,977
Okey. Satu, dua, tiga.

157
00:10:37,561 --> 00:10:39,814
- Aduh.
- Bertahan.

158
00:10:39,897 --> 00:10:42,316
Ke belakang pula, alahai.

159
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:43,692
Mintalah!

160
00:10:45,945 --> 00:10:48,572
Begini. Suruh dia bayar.

161
00:10:51,617 --> 00:10:53,452
Main tipu pula.

162
00:10:53,536 --> 00:10:54,662
Sekali lagi.

163
00:10:55,788 --> 00:10:57,164
Duit baki.

164
00:10:59,124 --> 00:11:00,125
Heon.

165
00:11:00,209 --> 00:11:03,963
Cikgu Moon suruh saya minta
awak syorkan bahan bacaan Inggeris.

166
00:11:04,547 --> 00:11:06,423
Katanya awak dah baca banyak buku.

167
00:11:06,507 --> 00:11:08,551
Saya baru bercadang untuk mula baca.

168
00:11:08,634 --> 00:11:10,386
Apa buku yang sesuai?

169
00:11:12,096 --> 00:11:14,557
- Saya akan sediakan senarai.
- Okey.

170
00:11:37,538 --> 00:11:39,290
Semua duit baju dah dikumpul?

171
00:11:39,373 --> 00:11:41,292
Cikgu minta sebelum kelas malam.

172
00:11:43,252 --> 00:11:44,587
Okey.

173
00:11:45,296 --> 00:11:46,630
- Jom.
- Ya.

174
00:12:11,030 --> 00:12:13,240
- Kenapa?
- Mana perginya?

175
00:12:14,491 --> 00:12:15,492
- Cuba ingat.
- Okey.

176
00:12:19,663 --> 00:12:21,540
Tolong hantar penilaian sastera.

177
00:12:27,838 --> 00:12:29,006
Nah.

178
00:12:29,089 --> 00:12:30,341
SHIN SOL-I

179
00:12:30,424 --> 00:12:31,884
Gila saya dibuatnya!

180
00:12:34,511 --> 00:12:36,764
Saya letak dalam buku sastera.

181
00:12:39,642 --> 00:12:40,684
Pergilah ambil.

182
00:12:40,768 --> 00:12:42,853
Ambil sebelum Hui-ji dan Su-jin tahu.

183
00:12:42,936 --> 00:12:45,189
Maksudnya,

184
00:12:45,272 --> 00:12:47,107
saya kena ke bilik guru.

185
00:12:47,191 --> 00:12:49,610
Tapi sebelah Cikgu Kim ada…

186
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:52,905
<i>Cikgu Cho.</i>

187
00:12:54,448 --> 00:12:56,367
Saya tak boleh ke sana.

188
00:13:04,124 --> 00:13:05,125
KANG HA-YOUNG
SHIN SOL-I

189
00:14:01,974 --> 00:14:03,058
Kawan.

190
00:14:03,892 --> 00:14:05,018
Apa?

191
00:14:05,102 --> 00:14:06,812
Kenapa? Awak tak sihat?

192
00:14:08,147 --> 00:14:09,189
Taklah.

193
00:14:10,649 --> 00:14:11,942
Perut saya sakit.

194
00:14:14,153 --> 00:14:15,237
Yakah?

195
00:14:28,834 --> 00:14:30,002
Helo, cikgu.

196
00:14:36,592 --> 00:14:39,553
Cikgu, perut saya sangat sakit.

197
00:14:40,054 --> 00:14:41,138
Tolong beri ubat.

198
00:14:42,473 --> 00:14:43,849
Bahagian mana yang sakit?

199
00:14:45,934 --> 00:14:47,019
Boleh cikgu periksa?

200
00:14:49,021 --> 00:14:50,064
Baiklah.

201
00:14:55,235 --> 00:14:56,570
Ini gastrik.

202
00:14:59,198 --> 00:15:00,991
Ini pula apendisitis.

203
00:15:06,205 --> 00:15:07,456
Maksudnya,

204
00:15:08,415 --> 00:15:11,126
- ubatnya juga berbeza?
- Betul.

205
00:15:11,210 --> 00:15:13,962
Rawatan dan ubat diberi
mengikut jenis penyakit.

206
00:15:14,046 --> 00:15:15,923
Jadi…

207
00:15:16,006 --> 00:15:16,882
Jantina juga penting.

208
00:15:18,133 --> 00:15:20,594
Ubat untuk lelaki dan wanita berbeza.

209
00:15:22,012 --> 00:15:23,764
Boleh beritahu cikgu dengan jelas?

210
00:15:29,269 --> 00:15:30,437
Kalau begitu,

211
00:15:31,146 --> 00:15:32,481
beri ubat untuk wanita.

212
00:15:47,121 --> 00:15:47,955
Terima kasih!

213
00:15:48,038 --> 00:15:50,040
Apa patut saya buat?

214
00:15:54,086 --> 00:15:55,003
Nah.

215
00:15:56,630 --> 00:15:57,965
Makan ubat ini.

216
00:16:03,804 --> 00:16:04,763
Apa?

217
00:16:06,056 --> 00:16:07,224
Makan cepat.

218
00:16:24,908 --> 00:16:26,285
Awak hilangkan duit baju?

219
00:16:27,077 --> 00:16:28,912
- Taklah.
- Yakah?

220
00:16:31,206 --> 00:16:33,167
- Baiklah.
- Heon!

221
00:16:34,918 --> 00:16:36,420
Tolonglah saya.

222
00:16:36,503 --> 00:16:39,381
- Kenapa pula?
- Maaf sebab tendang awak.

223
00:16:39,464 --> 00:16:41,341
Saya memang nak minta maaf.

224
00:16:42,426 --> 00:16:43,468
Jika awak tolong,

225
00:16:44,469 --> 00:16:46,221
saya akan ingat selamanya.

226
00:16:48,515 --> 00:16:49,641
Di mana duit itu hilang?

227
00:16:50,392 --> 00:16:52,102
Saya letak dalam buku sastera

228
00:16:52,186 --> 00:16:53,896
dan buku itu dah dihantar.

229
00:16:56,148 --> 00:16:57,149
Kalau begitu…

230
00:16:59,943 --> 00:17:02,696
awak boleh pergi tendang
cikgu sastera kita.

231
00:17:13,165 --> 00:17:15,792
Aduhai, habislah saya!

232
00:17:23,967 --> 00:17:26,553
Saya minta maaf. Saya merayu.

233
00:17:26,637 --> 00:17:29,723
Tolong jangan beritahu
kawan-kawan yang lain.

234
00:17:29,806 --> 00:17:32,643
Terutamanya Oh Hui-ji dan Lee Su-jin.

235
00:17:32,726 --> 00:17:34,186
Jangan beritahu mereka.

236
00:17:34,269 --> 00:17:37,022
Saya merayu.

237
00:17:37,105 --> 00:17:38,273
Awak buat apa?

238
00:17:39,191 --> 00:17:40,859
Kenapa berdiri di depan pintu?

239
00:17:47,908 --> 00:17:50,285
BILIK GURU

240
00:17:59,628 --> 00:18:02,130
Heon, awak okey?

241
00:18:02,714 --> 00:18:03,674
Cemburunya.

242
00:18:12,516 --> 00:18:14,101
Hui-ji, dah kumpul duit baju?

243
00:18:14,726 --> 00:18:16,728
Ya. Ada pada penolong ketua kelas.

244
00:18:21,566 --> 00:18:22,609
Sol-i, kenapa?

245
00:18:29,241 --> 00:18:31,994
Cikgu, sebenarnya…

246
00:18:33,495 --> 00:18:34,496
saya…

247
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,255
CHA HEON

248
00:19:07,362 --> 00:19:08,530
Sol-i?

249
00:19:13,410 --> 00:19:14,995
Cikgu, maafkan saya.

250
00:19:15,495 --> 00:19:17,914
Saya hilangkan duit baju

251
00:19:19,082 --> 00:19:21,418
dan Cha Heon yang temui duit itu.

252
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,670
Saya dah agak.

253
00:19:24,671 --> 00:19:26,131
Shin Sol-i, biar betul?

254
00:19:27,299 --> 00:19:28,550
Kawan-kawan, maaf.

255
00:19:29,801 --> 00:19:32,346
Nampaknya saya tak layak
jadi penolong ketua kelas.

256
00:19:32,846 --> 00:19:34,431
Dia patut letak jawatan.

257
00:19:34,514 --> 00:19:35,891
Ini kes besar.

258
00:19:37,851 --> 00:19:39,561
Dahsyat, bukan?

259
00:19:42,064 --> 00:19:43,482
Tolong senyap.

260
00:19:44,691 --> 00:19:46,526
Semua orang buat salah.

261
00:19:47,027 --> 00:19:49,112
Cikgu juga tak terkecuali.

262
00:19:49,196 --> 00:19:53,533
Tapi bukan mudah
untuk kita akui kesalahan kita.

263
00:19:54,409 --> 00:19:58,038
Kita juga perlukan keberanian untuk
tampil ke depan dan akui kesilapan kita.

264
00:19:59,039 --> 00:20:01,249
Oleh sebab itu, cikgu percaya

265
00:20:01,333 --> 00:20:03,168
Sol-i amat berani kerana mengaku.

266
00:20:07,214 --> 00:20:09,841
Duit itu tak hilang.

267
00:20:09,925 --> 00:20:11,385
Tak ada masalah, bukan?

268
00:20:12,594 --> 00:20:15,639
- Betul. Apa salahnya?
- Duit itu dah ditemui.

269
00:20:16,723 --> 00:20:17,557
Okey saja.

270
00:20:33,615 --> 00:20:40,247
BERSAMBUNG

271
00:20:42,290 --> 00:20:43,667
Heon, awak boleh pulang.

272
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:44,626
Silakan.

273
00:21:06,189 --> 00:21:08,275
Hei, apa itu?

274
00:21:09,401 --> 00:21:10,610
Tak ada apa, cikgu.

275
00:21:15,365 --> 00:21:17,951
Awak patut tumpukan perhatian.

276
00:21:18,618 --> 00:21:22,372
Dua tahun lagi, kamu semua
akan duduki peperiksaan. Faham?

277
00:21:25,459 --> 00:21:26,877
Faham, cikgu.

278
00:21:54,112 --> 00:21:56,907
Shin Sol-i, jangan putus asa!

279
00:21:57,491 --> 00:21:59,117
- Shun Sol-i!
- Heon!

280
00:22:00,577 --> 00:22:02,996
<i>- Saya ada hari sukan.
- Apa kaitannya dengan kamu?</i>

281
00:22:03,079 --> 00:22:05,415
<i>Heon, awak tahu
kenapa dia begitu bersungguh?</i>

282
00:22:05,499 --> 00:22:08,251
<i>Cikgu, Ha-young tak apa-apa, bukan?</i>

283
00:22:08,335 --> 00:22:09,252
<i>Saya kena pergi.</i>

284
00:22:09,336 --> 00:22:10,754
- Tak ada cara?
- Panjat pagar.

285
00:22:10,837 --> 00:22:12,172
<i>- Apa kamu semua buat?</i>
- Cikgu Cho datang.

286
00:22:12,255 --> 00:22:14,925
Nak jumpa sekejap
di taman permainan depan rumah?

287
00:22:15,592 --> 00:22:18,803
<i>- Jangan gementar.
- Heon, awak nak tolong saya?</i>

288
00:22:19,721 --> 00:22:24,726
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Hazizah Ali

